<h3><span class="chevron-closed">&nbsp;</span>Operations Lead</h3>
<div>
	<h5>Location</h5>
	<p>Philadelphia, PA or remote</p>
	<h5>About Girl Develop It</h5>
	<p>
		Girl Develop It is a 501(c)3 nonprofit organization that provides affordable and judgment-free opportunities for adult women interested in learning web and software development. Through in-person classes and community support, Girl Develop It helps women of diverse backgrounds achieve their technology goals and build confidence in their careers and their everyday lives.
	</p>
	<p>
		Girl Develop It is seeking a highly organized, experienced Operations Lead to design and execute strategy for the organization’s central operations, supporting 50+ chapters across the U.S.</p>
	<p>
	<h5>About this Role</h5>
	<p>
		The Operations Lead will be responsible for improving the overall operational infrastructure of Girl Develop It and providing crucial organizational support to our 52 chapters, 150+ chapter leaders and 60,000 students through collaboration with the Executive Director. Each month, GDI’s operational team manages payroll for 100+ instructors and organizers, and supports between 50-100 classes and events (involving 1,000+ transactions) serving women across the U.S. developing their technology skills. By the end of 2016, we expect to launch 10-15 additional chapters, evaluate the opportunity for international expansion and increase our membership to 100,000-120,000.
	</p>
	<p>
		The ideal candidate will have advanced experience streamlining and automating processes for a rapid-growth organization, and will be excited to jump in and help grow the organization’s capacity to scale sustainably.
	</p>
	<h5>Duties &amp; Responsibilities</h5>
	<p>
	<ul>
		<li>Lead day-to-day operational aspects of a mission-driven non-profit</li>
		<li>Drive organization-wide initiatives that contribute to long-term operational excellence in support of the mission of Girl Develop It</li>
		<li>Analyze and map current processes</li>
		<li>Provide and implement recommendations for streamlined growth</li>
		<li>Lead planning process for the organization's annual budget</li>
		<li>Administer HR functions, payroll, government compliance, taxes, etc. for Girl Develop It’s 2-5+ full-time staff, 150+ contractors and 40+ charitable state registrations</li>
		<li>Manage and facilitate transparency of organization budget and cashflow</li>
	</ul>
	</p>

