	<p>
	<ul>
		<li>Commitment to the mission of Girl Develop It</li>
		<li>Demonstrated experience leading operations</li>
		<li>Experience developing and overseeing organizational budgets</li>
		<li>Excellent computer skills and comfort with new technologies</li>
		<li>Proficiency in Google Apps (including Gmail, Drive, and Apps for Business)</li>
		<li>Comfort with Quickbooks (or equivalent double-entry accounting system)</li>
		<li>Excellent verbal and written communication skills</li>
		<li>Experience working as part of a distributed team (Optional if located in Philadelphia, PA)</li>
	</ul>
	</p>

